    public class MutualExclusionResourceImpl
extends ResourceImpl
implements MutualExclusionResource
    An implementation of the model object 'Mutual Exclusion Resource'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Protect Kind
    • Ceiling
    • Other Protect Protocol
    • Scheduler
